Jimp

JavaScript Image Manipulation Program

An image processing library for Node written entirely in JavaScript, with zero native dependencies

## Custom Jimp If you want to extend jimp or omit types or functions visit [@jimp/custom](./packages/custom). - Add file-types or switch encoder/decoders - Add add/remove plugins (image manipulation methods) ## Contributing Please read the [CONTRIBUTING documentation](CONTRIBUTING.md). ## Contributors ✨ Thanks goes to these wonderful people ([emoji key](https://allcontributors.org/docs/en/emoji-key)):
